data.description: Very nice 3 bed/ 2 bath 1999 Doublewide Mobile Home located near Maggie Valley off Jonathan Creek Rd. Large .625 acre lot with nice lawn and and mountain view. Plenty of room with 1560 square feet. Master bedroom with ensuite bath and large walk-in closet. City water with no city taxes. Overall good condition but does need some small repairs and cosmetic touches. Court ordered sale. 5% deposit required. 10 day upset bid period. Don't miss this opportunity to own a nice home at a reasonable price.
